in the last 50 years, @arbordayfoundation has planted and distributed nearly 500 million trees in more than 50 countries around the world to fight global issues facing humankind.

I have always had a love of the environment and admiration for trees and thus I try to find ways I can make a difference (big or small) to help the planet.

for each social media post with the hashtag #arborday from april 23-28, the arbor day foundation will be planting a tree, with the goal of planting 100,000 trees for the 150th anniversary of Arbor Day! (their main goal is to plant 500 million trees in the next five years)

at the studio, I got my face AI-scanned so they could design my custom AM & PM regime and facial based on my skin type! I still feel like I’m glowing post facial & just received my new skincare so I’m ecstatic to see how my skin responds. 

highly recommend checking out the new studio in the maria for the full relaxing REVEA experience!
